<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{locale}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{learnerName}}'s Learning Profile is Ready!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fc;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7C3AED 0%, #9F67FF 100%);
      padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .header p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .celebration-icon {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 32px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0E7FF 0%, #E8F5E9 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .highlight-box h3 {
      color: #7C3AED;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .highlight-box p {
      color: #4a5568;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .app-download-section {
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .app-download-section h3 {
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .store-buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .store-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .store-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .store-button.ios {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .store-button.android {
      background-color: #34A853;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .universal-link {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: #7C3AED;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .features-list {
      margin: 24px 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .features-list li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .features-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: #F0E7FF;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fc;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #7C3AED;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .store-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .store-button {
        width: 200px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="celebration-icon">üéâ</div>
      <h1>{{learnerName}}'s Learning Profile is Ready!</h1>
      <p>Their baseline assessment is complete</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hi {{parentName}},</p>

      <p>
        Great news! <strong>{{learnerName}}</strong> has completed their baseline assessment.
        We've created a personalized learning profile based on their unique strengths and areas for growth.
      </p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <h3>üß† What We Learned</h3>
        <p>
