          to understand how they think and learn best.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="app-download-section">
        <h3>üì± Download the Parent App</h3>
        <p>Stay connected to {{learnerName}}'s learning journey:</p>

        <div class="store-buttons">
          <a href="{{iosLink}}" class="store-button ios">
            üçé App Store
          </a>
          <a href="{{androidLink}}" class="store-button android">
            ü§ñ Google Play
