      <h4>With the Parent App you can:</h4>
      <ul class="features-list">
        <li>
          <span class="feature-icon">üìä</span>
          <span>View {{learnerName}}'s progress in real-time</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-icon">üéØ</span>
          <span>See personalized learning goals and achievements</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-icon">üí¨</span>
          <span>Receive updates on emotional well-being during sessions</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-icon">üèÜ</span>
          <span>Celebrate badges and milestones together</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-icon">üìù</span>
          <span>Review baseline results and adjust learning modules</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Once you've downloaded the app, sign in with this email address
        (<strong>{{parentEmail}}</strong>) to connect to {{learnerName}}'s account.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Questions? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@aivolearning.com">support@aivolearning.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>¬© {{currentYear}} AIVO Learning. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Manage notification preferences</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
